== The Man, The Myth, The Cuntwipe ==

Ryan Gentle is an uncontrollable fantastist, compulsive [[liar]], [[crap|amateur]] scammer, [[shit|part-time]] web designer, and full-time ''helmet''. He has been providing a consistently high quality of [[drama]] inside the UK [[anime]] [[loser|fan]] scene for many years now, his unbearable desire to [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Be_Somebody..._or_Be_Somebody%27s_Fool%21 "Be Somebody"] in the community and [[rape|prey on girls]] in the same instance, causing as much [[drama|mayhem]] as mirth, and is well worth learning more about.

When not stealing as much money as possible from his "[[gullible|friends]]", his trademark maneuver is to promise discount flights to [[Japan]], [[lie|supply free]] computers and webspace, and private conventions including the supposed booking of [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyde_Park%2C_London Hyde Park] for an outdoor anime showing to the younger (and slightly thicker) [[otaku]] on anime forums. When there are suggestions of foul play from more learned posters, [[pedobear|Ryan]] is often backed up by [[emo|kids]] who are easily deceived by his offers of free [[Pocky]], paid LiveJournal accounts, or perhaps an intoxicated fumbling [[rape]] in a tent.

Sightings of Ryan can be difficult to authenticate due to multiple aliases and profile information, but common elements are a location in either Plymouth, Liverpool, Birmingham or [[bullshit|Tokyo]], an occupation in sys-admin or web design, hobbies in the martial arts, and a birth date of December 17th 1986. In addition he continues to demonstrate he has ''no fucking idea'' that 'must of' and 'would/could/should of', and 'your' instead of 'you are/you're', are only used by ''completely illiterate fucking retards'' who don't understand that 'of' is ''fucking not a fucking verb and 'your' fucking indicates something fucking belonging to the second fucking '''person''', you fucking FUCK!''

