Guild members of Nightfall are presumed to be most susceptible to any future scams he may wish to employ. Watch out chaps!

It should be noted, that if you attempt to reveal his true identity to him, he'll get awfully upset and procede to ignore you. Usually this follows with him reporting you for gross neglegance of the WoW Terms and Conditions. Of course following any investigation, you are at no fault.

In any case, if you do encounter him in-game (which you will often do, as he has been '''VERY''' active since 2007, moreso recently), you are to be doing a service to the internet to, as stated above; '''GRIEF WITH EXTREME PREJUDICE!'''

